Name: JumpFist
About the game: Reclaim your games from the evil Pickle-Arms Johnson! Jumpfist is a fast paced platformer that will test even the most seasoned of gamers! Jump, punch, slide & elbow-drop your way through mayhem and reclaim your stolen games! You like fast paced platformers do you? You want a challenge you say? JumpFist is designed to test you, challenge you and yes....break you (legit i threw my controller down a few times beta testing) Jump, slide, punch and elbow drop your way through 40 levels! Too hard? Jump with a friend, local co-op available. Beat the developer times and become the fastest! Hilarious death commentary! JumpFist is here! Get that parkour today!
